1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Zhao An delivered the report last night — every word like a needle in his heart.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:14,000
Thirteen demons. A Hundred-Year Snake Demon. Ancient demonic blood. A Second-Rank Master.

3
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:19,000
A Second-Rank Master — one against a hundred on the battlefield.

4
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:25,000
And Lin Wan'er — the deposed concubine I exiled myself — wields such power?

5
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:32,000
What unsettles me more is six words — "ancient demonic blood".

6
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:38,000
If a human carries demonic blood — is she human, or demon?

7
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Zhao An — did your men see her kill?

8
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:50,000
The agents only saw the remains, Your Majesty — thirteen carcasses.

9
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:56,000
One was a six-meter Hundred-Year Snake Demon — its skull shattered by a single punch.

10
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:00,000
What else has she done?

11
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:07,000
She bound several minor demons as spies. And practices a frost art — ice spears that strike from ten paces.

12
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:13,000
Tell me — could she one day, do this to me?

13
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:20,000
Your Majesty — do not make her your enemy yet. Used right, she is a blade.

14
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:24,000
And if she cannot be used?

15
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:30,000
Then strangle her — before she grows beyond reach.

16
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:36,000
I need a blade. But a blade too sharp — will cut its wielder.

17
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:42,000
Keep watching her. And investigate another — Lin Huaiyuan.

18
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:48,000
I want to know what "strange ones" he met in the south.

19
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:54,000
Also — issue the order. In three days, I shall inspect the cold palace myself.

20
00:01:54,000 --> 00:02:00,000
I will see with my own eyes — what this Lady Lin has become.

21
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:07,000
He took the edict from the hidden compartment — read it long — then locked it away again.

22
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:13,000
Lin Wan'er — do not force my hand.

23
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:20,000
In three days, the Emperor walks into the cold palace — to see whether she is human, or demon.
